_IQ&oe=66E6D23D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Driven", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Immersive first person racing on the Meta Quest 2 & 3.\n\nCompete against AI to gain credits to purchase cars and gain access to races. Win the race to be added to the Global Leaderboards.\n\nTake part in Time Trials - navigate obstacles and get the fastest time on the Global Leaderboard.\n\nChallenging Race Series - take part in a number of races to win the Race Series - 30 Race Series in total\n\nOver 190 races to complete\nOver  30 cars to collect\nMultiplayer \nFreeroam\n\nDriven is a physics-based \"simcade\" racing game incorporating realistic car-handling and aerodynamics.\n\nVirtual steering and automatic or manual transmission.\n\n2 AI difficulty levels - extra credits awarded for racing against Pro AI.\n\nUpdated graphics for Quest 3\n\nNew Damage feature\n\n\nTake to the track and have fun!", "short_description": "Immersive first person racing on the Meta Quest 2 & 3\n\nCompete against AI to gain credits to purchase cars and gain access to races. Win the race to be added to Global Leaderboards\n\nTake part in Time Trial mode navigating obstacles - get on the Leaderboard\n\nVirtual steering and automatic/manual transmission.\n2 AI difficulty levels - extra credits awarded for racing against Pro AI\n\nUpdated graphics for Quest 3\nDamage feature"}]}, "developer_name": "MK1", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://mk1vrracing.wixsite.com/driven", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "MK1", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://mk1vrracing.wixsite.com/driven", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_FEW", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "673385183287495"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["RACING", "AC